description:
KICKING OFF INOKANS , which is a new series I am starting that focuses on playing with negative spaces, geometric shapes, and imaginative subjects. It's very open on the end result, so expect some variety ranging from animation, 3d, digital painting and others.

And what a better way to kick off this series by taking part in the #objkt4objkt. Thank you in advance for collecting this work. I really appreciate it. Stay tuned for more works to come.

3508x4961 / 300 DPI
